{
  "stem": "16106.6",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At first, [INAUDIBLE], and then I get [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there I met [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we went to his kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had the most glorious uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had a big Australian hat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it has-- [INAUDIBLE] in the war, they wore those watches which had leather covers [? the ?] up and down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was fabulously sexy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they had-- and they had those things that were covered so they shouldn't shine?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I thought it was so sexy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Had this big Australian hat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had dogs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, we-- we really got on very well, had lots of fun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Emanuel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kahn.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You want to hear about my wedding?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we-- I then moved to his kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], which was a little-- it was a different political thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was [INAUDIBLE], and [INAUDIBLE] was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I moved to that kibbutz, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I lived in a tent with our dog.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and then-- in those days, it was like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't get married before, before-- married was moving into a [INAUDIBLE], into a family room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was considered officially married, even not with a rabbi, OK?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when you got pregnant, you had to go to the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there was a condition to go to the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It had to be winter, when there has no work to do on the fields.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You had to have more than one pregnant lady.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was during the war, mind you, more or less, during the war, '48.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had to be more pregnant, so it's worth the gasoline.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then you had to have a free truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then you had to go to the next kibbutz, where there was an old gentleman who was a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
